flowRoot.flowPara: The old Skype module is replaced by the Social Networks module which allows to add the identifiers of the latter in the fields of the corresponding networks: facebook, skype and twitter on the cards of your contacts .

The old Skype module is replaced by the Social Networks module which allows to add the identifiers of the latter in the fields of the corresponding networks: facebook, skype and twitter on the cards of your contacts .
We now have the possibility to create a backup file in the administration containing all the documents, pdf, images etc. created by Dolibarr or added by the users.

The old Skype module is replaced by the Social Networks module which allows to add the identifiers of the latter in the fields of the corresponding networks: facebook, skype and twitter on the cards of your contacts.
Dolibarr now offers the possibility : to create websites, to integrate an existing website on Dolibarr, to import and export full websites.
This feature allows you to define e-mail sending templates. Now you can add the following substitution variables in the email templates: Day D and Month M.

text.tspan: New on Entering a Client Rule

flowRoot.flowPara: The column that informs about the deadline of a payment has been added
In the Events / Agenda tab we can now know if the resource is available
You now have the option of exporting FEC-formatted journal entry files (as per Article L47A of the Tax Procedures Book) into the Advanced Accounting module configuration.
Added a workforce filter in the Third Party module on the Customer List, This allows companies to be filtered by the number of employees seized.
You can now associate a project with a salary settlement. This allows you to add an expense within the project.
Addition of the supplier product reference on the receipt of a supplier order.
Addition of the supplier product reference on the receipt of a supplier order.
It is now possible to sort the invoice lines by EEC member or not in the related invoice lines
Addition of the option " offset " in the configurations. This option is used to customize the due date for an invoice .

You can now highlight the line you have selected in a list and set the color you want in display configurations by selecting a color code in the Color section of the highlight line when the mouse is overhead.
You can now add all rights to all modules in one click to a group or user.
You now have the opportunity to simplify the Dolibarr interface for the visually impaired.
The interface is visually different and adapted for the visually impaired.
It has gone into stable - it can simplify the creation of plugin in Dolibarr.
Allows documents to be shared in the " Documents" module of Dolibarr via the DAV module (standard webdav protocol).
Possibility of adding a mandatory field on Dolibarr forms. To do this, simply add the name of the field in the configurations.
It is now possible to specify whether the additional attribute should be included in the lists.
We now have the possibility to create a backup file in the administration containing all the documents, pdf, images etc. created by Dolibarr or added by the users (made by atm_logo_petit ).
Added a hidden option to not modify the default validator when creating an expense report: EXPENSEREPORT_DEFAULT_ VALIDATOR_UNCHANGEABLE
Allows you to automatically add the commercial tracking proposal as a contact on the quote: PROPOSAL_AUTO_ADD_AUTHOR_AS_ CONTACT
